These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
Music-Genre: country, techno, punk, blues
Cigar: montecristo, prince, oliveros, tiparillo
1. Cigar:tiparillo is on the left of Music-Genre:punk##1
2. Music-Genre:country is on the left of Cigar:prince##1
3. Music-Genre:blues is in an odd position##4
4. Cigar:oliveros is on the left or right of Cigar:tiparillo##3
5. Music-Genre:country is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | country | techno | blues | punk |
| Cigar        | montecristo | prince   | tiparillo | oliveros    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
Flower: zinnia, balloon-flower, dahlia, azalea
City: venice, rome, prague, london
1. Flower:balloon-flower is on the left of Flower:azalea##1
2. City:venice is on the left of City:prague##1
3. City:prague is in an odd position##4
4. City:venice == Flower:zinnia##1
5. City:rome is on the right of City:prague##1
6. City:venice == Flower:zinnia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Flower   | dahlia | zinnia  | balloon-flower  | azalea |
| City   | london    | venice | prague | rome    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
Music-Genre: house, gospel, dubstep, folk
Transport: tram, ship, bike, scooter
1. Music-Genre:folk is on the left or right of Transport:scooter##3
2. Music-Genre:dubstep is in an even position##4
3. Transport:scooter is on the left or right of Music-Genre:gospel##3
4. Transport:scooter is on the right of Transport:bike##1
5. Transport:tram is in an odd position##4
6. Music-Genre:gospel is on the right of Music-Genre:dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Music-Genre          | folk | dubstep | gospel    | house      |
| Transport   | bike        | scooter     | tram | ship |

