.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
Movie-Genre: crime, thriller, family, documentary
Beverage: lemonade, milk, water, 7up
1. Movie-Genre:thriller is between Beverage:lemonade and Beverage:7up##2
2. Movie-Genre:documentary is on the left of Movie-Genre:crime##1
3. Beverage:water is in an odd position##4
4. Beverage:milk is on the left of Beverage:7up##1
5. Beverage:milk is on the right of Movie-Genre:crime##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre         | documentary | crime | thriller | family |
| Beverage   | water       | lemonade   | milk    | 7up  |

