2. Movie-Genre:documentary == Pet:dog##1
3. Movie-Genre:zombie is on the right of Pet:guinea-pig##1
4. Pet:hamster is on the far left##1
5. Pet:cat is in an odd position##4
6. Movie-Genre:thriller is on the far left or far right##3

