.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
Beverage: water, iced-tea, hot-chocolate, tea
Sport: biathlon, soccer, cricket, rugby
1. Beverage:iced-tea is in an even position##4
2. Beverage:iced-tea is on the left or right of Sport:biathlon##3
3. Sport:soccer is between Beverage:water and Sport:biathlon##2
4. Beverage:iced-tea is on the far left or far right##3
5. Sport:cricket is on the right of Beverage:tea##1
6. Sport:cricket is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Beverage         | water | hot-chocolate   | tea | iced-tea |
| Sport   | rugby          | soccer | biathlon         | cricket  |

 